<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>2024 on Kaya Log</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/tags/2024/</link><description>Recent content in 2024 on Kaya Log</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yshghid.github.io/tags/2024/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>github blog 커스텀하기: archive 창 수정</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/hugo/hugo-custom3/</link><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/study/hugo/hugo-custom3/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="github-blog-커스텀하기-archive-창-수정">
 github blog 커스텀하기: archive 창 수정
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#github-blog-%ec%bb%a4%ec%8a%a4%ed%85%80%ed%95%98%ea%b8%b0-archive-%ec%b0%bd-%ec%88%98%ec%a0%95">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/06aaccaa-8c31-43e4-9815-6924dc00589b" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>hugo-book 테마에서 tag, category에 따른 archive창을 볼수있는데 위와같이 구성돼있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>내용없이 제목만 뜨게 만들고싶어서 &lt;a href="https://github.com/alex-shpak/hugo-book/tree/master/layouts">hugo-book 테마의 layout 디렉토리&lt;/a>를 찾아보니 &lt;a href="https://github.com/alex-shpak/hugo-book/blob/master/layouts/taxonomy/taxonomy.html">taxonomy/taxonomy.html&lt;/a>과 &lt;a href="https://github.com/alex-shpak/hugo-book/blob/master/layouts/posts/list.html">post/list.html&lt;/a>이 관여하고있는듯해서, 내 리포지토리에 taxonomy/taxonomy.html과 layouts/post/list.html을 생성해서 각각 다음과 같이 작성해주었다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{{ define &amp;#34;main&amp;#34; }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> {{ range sort .Paginator.Pages }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672">article&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">class&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;markdown book-post&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672">h2&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672">a&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">href&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;{{ .RelPermalink }}&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&amp;gt;{{ partial &amp;#34;docs/title.html&amp;#34; . }}&amp;lt;/&lt;span style="color:#f92672">a&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &amp;lt;/&lt;span style="color:#f92672">h2&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> {{ partial &amp;#34;docs/post-meta&amp;#34; . }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &amp;lt;/&lt;span style="color:#f92672">article&lt;/span>&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> {{ end }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> {{ template &amp;#34;_internal/pagination.html&amp;#34; . }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{{ end }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{{ define &amp;#34;toc&amp;#34; }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> {{ partial &amp;#34;docs/taxonomy&amp;#34; . }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>{{ end }}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>참고로 위코드는 원래코드에서 아래 내용을 뺀것이다.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>